Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:10.66,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Knights is an \Nelite group of Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:44.10,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The selection exam to choose \Nits members has finally begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:49.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, along with Mimosa Vermillion \Nand the mysterious mage Xerx LÃ¼gner,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:51.32,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,head into their first \Nbattle of the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:55.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:58.18,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, Xerx doesn't seem \Ninterested in fighting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:02.18,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Annoyed by this, Asta and Mimosa decide \Nto attack the enemy camp on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:03.16,main,Curtis,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:06.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though Asta's team \Nwas going to lose, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:11.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The trap spells that Xerx set activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:14.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and they managed to completely \Nturn things around into a victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the one who appeared \Nin the second match...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:18.98,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You're not beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:23.25,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best not to taint my beauty, \Nfor I am Kirsch Vermillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:49.04,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(187,1)}Fierce Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.56,italicstop,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... life is so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:03:00.91,sign_4194_20_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(732,1)\blur3}C Team\NThe Coral Peacocks 1st Class Senior Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Kirsch Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:01.60,italicstop,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this world filled \Nwith such unsightly things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:06.81,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, why was I born so beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:07.70,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.29,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd this weirdo come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:14.39,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I just... Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:16.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're so insanely creepy, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.65,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such despair, you ugly creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:23.14,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you must be \Nquite jealous of my beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.13,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,but there are things that \Njust can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:29.07,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you calling ugly?! \NWhat even is this conversation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.81,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get dropped on your \Nhead when you were born?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.47,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The only one that's beautiful \Nis Sis, and Sis alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:38.19,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You're so gross, you narcissist creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:43.14,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,A maiden shouldn't use such vulgar words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:48.20,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Your proportions are somewhat \Non the beautiful side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.57,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Why not learn from me to better yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.04,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that team going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.67,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if it isn't Mimosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:02.09,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to admire my beauty, \Nmy beloved little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:05.64,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let my beauty cause your heart to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:10.14,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say you're beautiful. \NYou're so narcissistic that it's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.57,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Mimosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.86,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell how beautiful I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.65,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sick? Let me cure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.17,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you're the one \Nthat's sick, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.70,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I actually want you to \Nlose this upcoming round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.28,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You were never good at telling jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.74,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.96,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Jokes should be told with \Nmore elegance and beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:35.24,top,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! As beautiful as I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:39.20,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa's older bro is, like... sparkly. \NOr I guess I should say... unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.58,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.38,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess Mimosa's been \Nthrough some hard times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, heya. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa's always been so kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.93,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the peasant known as Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:56.98,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me as though \Nwe're friends, you swine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! His eyes suddenly died!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.68,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the sight of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.95,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Neither your mannerisms nor \Nbehavior are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.82,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence is unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.70,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Your clothes are filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.95,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,To top everything off, your muscles are ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:19.12,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Bodies should be beautiful just as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.71,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see why you would train them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.13,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Only the weak would do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I didn't have any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I trained!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They might be unsightly, \Nbut these are my weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:41.53,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The size of the vessel into \Nwhich an individual's mana
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.77,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,is poured is determined from birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:47.49,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Unsightly struggling won't change its shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Vessel... Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:57.45,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,How could someone as unsightly \Nas you become a Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:01.39,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Kirsch, please win this match,\N no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:04.63,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mimosa! To think you'd say such words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.09,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you finally fully understand my charms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:12.34,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Because Asta and I intend to \Nslaughter you in the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.01,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Slaughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.06,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Such an unsightly word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:24.44,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that sparkly guy? I can see \Nhim from all the way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.74,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,All that sparkling is sort of wasted on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kirsch Vermillion. \NHe's Mimosa's older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.15,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,To describe him in a single \Nword... He's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.45,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.85,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Vice Captain of the Coral Peacocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.22,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sell him short!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.46,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how he looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:43.10,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,in place of their captain who's \Nalways asleep, Dorothy Unsworth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:46.05,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he does almost all of\Nthe squad's practical magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:50.67,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,"Despite how he looks." So you \Nthink he's weird, too, four-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Four-eyes sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:53.85,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Four-eyes definitely does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.47,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:57.60,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.82,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,When's the next match going to begin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.85,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,How long do they intend to make me wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:04.92,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.40,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The next battle will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:15.12,sign_10224_102_Sol___Kirsch___M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sol   Kirsch   Magna
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:15.12,sign_10224_103_C_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}C Team
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:15.12,sign_10224_104_Cesc___Adrian___,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Cesc   Adrian   Willy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:15.12,sign_10224_105_D_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}D Team
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:13.00,top,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,C Team: Kirsch, Sol, and Magna \Nversus D Team: Cesc, Adrian, and Willy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.12,top,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Let the second match begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.87,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Now... let me show you \Nhow truly beautiful I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.21,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry up and get back so \Nwe can cheer Magna and the others on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.96,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta's so close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:33.29,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You seem unfazed, you shitty little shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:36.61,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be facing \Nthem next if they win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Xerx...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.50,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:45.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That you didn't come here to win. \NThat you had a certain goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.65,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:53.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide anything from us. You piss \Nme off, but you're our teammate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:59.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make sure we \Nwin by working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:00.62,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.25,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll need you to work hard \Nas the decoy next round, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not exactly working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.38,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:19.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Grand Slam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm gonna waste any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:29.32,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If I just go right in there and bust \Nthe shit out of that crystal, we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.45,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What a fantastic spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.88,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,A fifth-class junior peasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:42.04,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Just barging in there \Nwithout a plan? He's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.71,main,Cesc,0000,0000,0000,,Shakudo Magic: Pursuing Jackals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.01,main,Cesc,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:59.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I see you, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat the crap out of all \Nthese things, then beat the shit out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.06,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,What a crude way of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.03,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,So unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.61,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did you pop up from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.08,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You're straining too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:19.65,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You're blessed with the ability to \Nuse both close and long-range magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.16,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Your mana is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.54,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:26.67,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Read the flow of the enemy's mana more.\NLet your mana be your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:30.29,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,and use close and long-range \Nattacks at the appropriate times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:34.65,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be able to burn \Nmore beautifully than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:40.30,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Using close and long-range magic \Nat the appropriate times...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:45.15,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't strain so much... And read \Nthe enemy's flow of mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.86,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the closer \Nones first. Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.00,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the one that's \Nall the way back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where'd that sparkly bastard go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:15.26,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Creation Magic: Raging Mother Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.01,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:22.01,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show you guys what I can do to \Nraise our squad's rank and make Sis happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.51,main,Willy,0000,0000,0000,,Mud Binding Magic: Flash Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.06,main,Willy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you go that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.77,main,Willy,0000,0000,0000,,You and your golem can \Nget sucked into my bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.73,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:37.32,main,krisch,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I surrounded by such \Nsloppy and simple-minded people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:42.28,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Magic which creates golems that \Ncan be given certain orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:47.26,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Since this isn't a feint, \Nits size is unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.79,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, ya jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:53.03,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Why not split it up into smaller ones \Nand use them to cause confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:56.30,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,It would be beautiful to have them \Nlie in ambush within the earth, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.86,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that with your \Nunique mana, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.55,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:07.31,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Creation Magic: Divided Mother Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.48,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Mobility over power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:14.06,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna get caught in that bog again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:21.39,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I shall guard the crystal! Therefore, \Nit shall remain beautiful and unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:24.50,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Bloom as gloriously as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:29.33,main,Adrian,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NYour crystal's been left completely unguarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:34.75,main,Adrian,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Climbing Coelacanth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.17,main,Adrian,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.21,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:47.97,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You're already captives \Nof my beautiful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.54,top,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry Blossom Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:54.98,sign_16988_180_Cherry_Blossom_M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(960,1)}Cherry Blossom Magic: Magic Cherry Blossom Storm of Petals\N{\fs18} ~Plus My Beautiful Illusion~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:54.98,top,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Cherry Blossom Storm of Petals \NPlus My Beautiful Illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:12:00.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That whole area's covered \Nin a storm of petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.45,main,Willy,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap! I can't see where our enemies are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.74,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:11.20,italics,All,0000,0000,0000,,...a road that leads straight to the crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.96,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth unto the beautiful \Nprimrose path to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.71,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:22.13,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Bloom! Bloom! Bloom! Bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.59,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Fully bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:27.23,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.86,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,C Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.43,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.44,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, sin is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.91,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,being unsightly, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.11,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...failing to notice beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.92,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We somehow got pulled into his bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.99,italics,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off, but it feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:52.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast! And unbelievably strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:57.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to beat \Nthem in the next battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:03.84,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... the greatest sin of all is my beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.51,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How was our fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.43,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.99,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.23,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.69,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell did I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.32,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:28.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That spell... First, he produced \Nvarious clones to confuse the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.78,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Then he covered the battlefield \Nin a storm of magic petals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.62,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,making it hard to see or detect magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:38.58,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, it created a safe route to \Nthe enemy crystal for his teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.96,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The only way that's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:43.42,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,is because being royalty gives \Nyou a monstrous amount of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.72,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... My beauty scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:51.11,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The man closest to becoming the next \Ncaptain of the Coral Peacocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:53.66,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Kirsch Vermillion. Quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.73,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But he's still a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:01.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That magic was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Mimosa's bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mention that, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.89,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, swine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.82,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You're dirtying my space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:15.87,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You're next. A broken vessel \Nlike you who can't use magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:18.87,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use my magic to shatter the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:25.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how, but apparently when a \Nvessel's cracked, you can use it longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.01,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Cracked?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:31.21,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You were only using that \Nvessel because you're poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.36,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:39.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That cracked vessel was something \NSister bought for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's the symbol of love \Nbetween Sister Lily and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep using it forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.99,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, this was all just a "what if."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.23,Default,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Your brain is unsightly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is round three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:59.21,sign_10224_102_Sol___Kirsch___M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Finral  Leopold  Hamon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:59.21,sign_10224_103_C_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}E Team
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:59.21,sign_10224_104_Cesc___Adrian___,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kyle   Borja   Gaston
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:59.21,sign_10224_105_D_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}F Team
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:59.21,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,E Team: Finral, Leopold, and Hamon versus \NF Team: Kyle, Borja, and Gaston.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.34,sign_4194_20_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Crimson Lion Kings Intermediate Magic Knight Second Class\N{\fs30}Leopold Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:03.34,top,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit 'em fast and \Nloud with my flame magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:07.59,sign_4194_20_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Golden Dawn Intermediate Magic Knight Second Class\N{\fs30}Hamon Caseus
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:08.17,top,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,No, let us attack them with elegant \Nflair using my glass magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:13.64,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Kirsch fight has lit a fire within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.06,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Let us also settle this beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.19,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:22.07,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,If you've been lit aflame, I'll use my \Nflames to light an even greater flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:23.90,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Kirsch is gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.94,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:31.97,sign_4194_20_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(926,1040)}The Black Bulls Junior Magic Knight First Class\N{\fs30}Finral Roulacase
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:28.26,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Could you leave our attack strategy to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.73,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial magic gives you incredible mobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.32,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason not to use that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:37.09,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't fought alongside \Nthe Black Bulls for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.18,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.69,italics,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:48.71,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! Let's see you bring \Nout the best in us then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.67,main,Gaston,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold and Hamon are both quite skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.38,main,Gaston,0000,0000,0000,,Go after the trash from the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.89,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:07.07,italics,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,His spatial magic is pretty useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:09.77,main,Gaston,0000,0000,0000,,Borja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:12.36,main,Borja,0000,0000,0000,,Feather Magic: Feather Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.99,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:14.91,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.37,main,Borja,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.34,italics,Gaston,0000,0000,0000,,Curses... Friendly fire was \Ntheir goal all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:38.76,italics,Gaston,0000,0000,0000,,And flame magic is an attribute\N I'm weak against on top of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:43.39,italics,Gaston,0000,0000,0000,,That spatial magic user has a \Ngood eye on this battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:49.40,italics,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,He knows where our magic works best and takes\N us to the perfect point on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:53.70,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Glass Creation Magic: Verre ÃpÃ©e!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:59.70,italics,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the Black Bulls\N had someone this good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.25,italics,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he stay hidden for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:07.25,italics,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I can attack \Nwith all the power I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:10.92,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.22,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal destroyed! E Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.51,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.89,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we won, but man, was I nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.39,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:27.90,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,We should have a meal after a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:32.80,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! Let's see who can eat the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.50,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely not in the \Nmood for that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah... ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.86,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The way he uses his spatial \Nmagic is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.75,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's still a junior Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.26,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Black Bulls in this exam so \Nfar have been junior Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.30,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't taken them seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.13,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but the last two Black Bulls\N also exhibited powers
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.18,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,that seemed beyond juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.10,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the Black Bulls really \Nare different this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:04.77,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for the guy who brought \Nshame upon the House of Vaude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:08.21,italics,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you exactly how \Ndifferent we are next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.98,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is round four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:18.11,sign_10224_104_Cesc___Adrian___,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gareth   Simon   Medeo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:18.11,sign_10224_105_D_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}H Team
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:18.11,sign_10224_102_Sol___Kirsch___M,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Langris   Flagil   Sekke
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:18.11,sign_10224_103_C_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}G Team
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:18.11,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,G Team: Langris, Flagil, and Sekke versus \NH Team: Gareth, Simon, and Medeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.90,italicstop,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Bah-ha, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:24.89,sign_4194_20_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(960,996)}The Green Praying Mantises Junior Magic Knight Fifth Class\N{\fs30}Sekke Bronzazza
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.20,italicstop,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here is ridiculously strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.24,italicstop,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It was too early for me \Nto do this exam, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.12,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what the heck \Nwas up with Captain Jack being all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:31.98,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's give the newbies a chance, too"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.51,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:36.37,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did I get picked, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:40.01,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I said I could do it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.82,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:47.06,top,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls so far have been \Namazing despite being juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:49.02,sign_4194_20_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(941,1)}The Aqua Deer Intermediate Magic Knight Third Class\N{\fs30}Flagil Tormenta
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.02,top,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably also strong, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:52.21,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! I'm surprised you saw through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.27,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,What to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:57.90,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like standing out, \Nbut I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:05.74,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,First off, why don't I go rampaging \Nin on my Sekke Shooting Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.18,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.58,top,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a great plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.58,sign_4194_20_C_Team_The_Coral,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The Golden Dawn Vice Captain\N{\fs30}Langris Vaude
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:16.84,main,Gareth,0000,0000,0000,,All right. The crystal is completely \Ncovered with a barrier spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.09,main,Gareth,0000,0000,0000,,No one can destroy it easily now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.92,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:30.23,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.18,italics,Gareth,0000,0000,0000,,They're charging straight at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.36,italics,Gareth,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that lame vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.40,main,Simon,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:39.37,main,Medio,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can fall for the trap \Nspells we set in the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He shaved the space away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:09.60,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The crystal's been destroyed. G Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.98,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Did you all witness that elegant rampage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.48,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one with the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.99,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.22,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the House of Vaude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.24,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:31.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... That's Finral's younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:35.50,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Could I cut magic like that with my sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.00,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:43.92,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you'll never be more than \Na means of transportation, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:49.13,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,In our upcoming match, be careful not to \Nget in the way of my spatial magic, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:52.37,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee that you \Nwon't lose something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:57.06,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,If that were to happen, \NMother and Father aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.31,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that she would be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:05.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So to ensure that doesn't happen,\N I'm going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:09.15,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,How insolent of you, Brother.
