Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:43.86,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:47.88,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}I Can See It!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:45.91,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I Can See It!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:51.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Finral! \NYou can see the whole battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your field of vision is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm lucky enough to have \NCaptain Yami train me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:22:58.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What kind of training is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:01.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,For example, after a meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:03.15,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heave ho, heave ho, heave ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:07.24,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The way he's patting his belly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.46,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You must need to use the bathroom!\N Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:14.53,sign_33322_360_Bathroom_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:14.53,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That annoyed way he's knocking on the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:15.58,sign_33436_362_Bathroom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx352\fry38}Bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:16.99,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You must be out of toilet paper! Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:19.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Other than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:20.66,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:24.54,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your coffee milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:27.76,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure your mustache \Nlooks wild enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:30.38,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not too clean-shaven and not too rugged!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:34.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's just getting used.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:37.34,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.67,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm here to dazzle you\N with my beauty again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:44.41,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,You were so beautifully happy \Nwhen I beautifully spread beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:46.27,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,across the battlefield \Nbecause I'm so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:51.11,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The even more beautiful {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, \Nbeautiful Page 76: "Mage X."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 76\N\N{\fs18} Mage X
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:53.82,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,My beauty knows no bounds.
